title: S1 E90: Lights Out in Six Minutes and Counting
description:
Things go from worse to worst inside Whittier and Cyrus is forced to take matters into his own hands.
Holiday and Cyrus hack into Whittier’s database where they discover something shocking about Holiday’s past.
